General.Name: Selcuk Gida Endustri Ihracat Ithalat AS
General.Description: Selçuk Gida Endüstri Ihracat Ithalat A.S. produces and sells dried fruits in Turkey. It offers dried figs, raisins, apricots, mulberries, and cherries; and energy balls and energy discs under the EAGLE brand and various private labels through hyper-supermarkets and discount chains. The company also exports its products to approximately 30 countries. Selçuk Gida Endüstri Ihracat Ithalat A.S. was founded in 1932 and is based in Izmir, Turkey.
